# Technology Stack

## Core Technologies
- React 19
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- TypeScript 5
- TailwindCSS 4

## Development Tools
- ESLint 9
- Prettier 3
- Husky 9
- lint-staged 15

## Testing Stack
- Vitest
- Playwright

## Node Version
- Node.js 22.x (Volta managed)

## Package Manager
- pnpm (preferred)

## Development Commands
```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Start development server with Turbopack
pnpm dev

# Build for production
pnpm build

# Run linting
pnpm lint

# Fix linting issues
pnpm lint:fix

# Format code
pnpm prettier
